import { IconLogo, NavbarContainer, NavbarWrapper } from "./Navbar.elements"
import { AiFillAlipayCircle } from "react-icons/ai";

const Navbar = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <NavbarContainer>
                <NavbarWrapper>
                    <IconLogo>
                        <AiFillAlipayCircle />
                        Javi-p(x)
                    </IconLogo>
                </NavbarWrapper>
            </NavbarContainer>
        </>
    )
}

export default Navbar
